# Cricket Score Lower Third Template

Professional cricket score lower third graphics designed for live sports production, tournament coverage, digital streaming, and broadcast workflows.

This template demonstrates a production-ready approach to presenting real-time cricket scores, team information, overs, wickets, and match status within a compact lower-third graphics format suitable for modern sports broadcasts.

---

## Overview

Score lower thirds are among the most frequently triggered graphics during cricket coverage. They provide immediate match context while preserving maximum visibility of on-field action.

This template showcases a modular score presentation workflow that can be adapted for:

* International cricket broadcasts
* Domestic leagues
* Franchise tournaments
* Club cricket streaming
* School and university competitions
* OTT sports productions

