## Graphics Architecture

The template follows a layered graphics approach consisting of:

### Primary Information Layer

* Team names
* Current score
* Wickets
* Overs

### Secondary Information Layer

* Match status
* Required run rate
* Partnership information
* Tournament identifiers

### Branding Layer

* Competition branding
* Sponsor assets
* Broadcaster identity elements

